<br>
If you ever happen to look up books on Angels(this includes good and evil ones) you will see that the Diablo series has plenty to cover when it comes to making the next Evil guy...lol.<br>
<br>
But all and all, I'm hoping that they decide to take the whole series to the next level. And that would be just making Diablo Online. The game would be extremly popular. <br>
<br>
If I could be one to develop such a project I would keep the 2D and a half interface. Don't get me wrong, Everquest looks cool and all, but after working at Nintendo I got really sick of everything going 3D. Thats why I thought that Ultima Online was cool, one of the only reasons I thought it was cool...lol. <br>
<br>
It is rumored that eventually we will see a Fallout Online someday. If you have ever played Fallout or Fallout 2, you know that those games were a blast. You would also know that they used the same graphic view as the Diablo series.<br>
<br>
I just look forward to the day when thousands and thousands can be on one server and one game together with Diablo. To see an interactive world with Guildhouses, real players occupying houses, wars with hundred going at each other, it would be the best game ever. <br>
<br>
Also adding the changing quest idea to the game like Everquest would just be awesome. Who knows what would be going on from day to day. <br>
<br>
Well I better quit this one before I get the urge to play Ultima or EQ again......<br>
<br>
Sir Michael<br>
